# Same methodological inputs (mechanical-clock-time-measurement observatories with sultanic / royal patronage, comparable instrumentation, contemporaneous 1576-1580) — divergent institutional outcomes (Uraniborg succeeds + transmits to Kepler/Newton; Istanbul Observatory destroyed by political-religious veto). The divergence is most informative when prior assumptions are documented per institution.
